This means, at least in this case, that he has opted to participate in all 16 contests.
In other words, a design for one of the doors to clash in program and definition with that of the architect of the next door.
In his opinion, yes, the town hall should ensure that the strip immediately above Ronda de Dalt should provide, in its entirety, a facility area that makes a smooth transition between the city and the green.
