We won't even go so far as to write that there was collusion between them, but the image is symbolic.
Sitting side by side on the podium of the Stade de France auditorium, Georges Leekens and Eden Hazard made peace.
Five months after the gesture of his striker against Turkey, the Belgian coach has nothing but praise to say about him.
"I am very happy with Eden, his progress and the fact that he is Belgian".
